node.text: @emmabeasor no babe it was just concrete, I’m glad you weren’t there to see it x
Love those tiles. Mine were all gone by the time I moved in 😭

Decided I don't have enough on so decided to move house and do a full refurb but the things we have found are brilliant such as original tiles 🙌🏻 Fergie and Maggie Thatcher on a 90s paper, a young David Bailey at fashion week and even a newspaper from 1961. Let the renovation begin...and the end of my marriage (oh and I'm living with mum for 6 months so that should make @tablemannerspodcast serie 8 a Whopper for high drama!) X (ps my marriage is not over!!! Judging from your comments my caption was poorly written!!)
Forget 90’s daily mail... you’ll be a 90’s attitude teenager living at your mums in 5,4,3,2,1 😂😂😂❤️❤️❤️
Connecting with THIS post on just a whole bunch 'a levels pwoah
R u a Virgo

Once good thing, I’m having help with my 10month old at times! P.S CANNOT WAIT for the new podcast to start, I’ve really missed it, especially since your teaser of three episodes at Edinburgh! Xxxx
